  Commission Meeting and Hearing Schedule

   Public Hearings are scheduled for February 25, 2002; February 26, 2002;
   and March 19, 2002. The tentative times for the hearings are as
   follows: 3:00 to 5:00 p.m. on February 25, 2002; 9:30 to 11:30 a.m. on
   February 26, 2002; and 3:00 to 5:00 p.m. on March 19, 2002. Important
   information concerning dates, times, and deadlines.

   June 19 - Public Hearing, Rapids City, South Dakota
   August 27-28 - Briefing Session and Public Meeting
   September 10 - Briefing Session and Public Meeting
   October 25-26 - Briefing Session
   November 13 - 14 - Briefing Session and Public Meeting
   December 3-4 - Briefing Session
   January 8-9, 2002 - Briefing Session and Public Meeting

   (All meeting & hearing locations are Washington, DC, unless otherwise
   noted.)

